81075>>>>>    //***
81075>>>>>
81075>>>>>    Procedure SeedDataSources
81077>>>>>        Local String  sDriver
81077>>>>>        Local String  sVoid
81077>>>>>        Local Integer iRetval
81077>>>>>
81077>>>>>        Get psDriverID To sDriver
81078>>>>>        If (sDriver <> "") ;            Call_Driver 0 sDRiver Function CLI_INITDATASOURCES Callback 0 Passing sVoid sVoid SQL_FETCH_ALL Result iRetval
81085>>>>>    End_Procedure // SeedDataSources
81086>>>>>
81086>>>>>
81086>>>>>
81086>>>>>    //***
81086>>>>>    //*** Function: DataSources
81086>>>>>    //*** Purpose : Call the driver's data sources function
