81359>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @Param  FieldNumber           Number of the field
81359>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @Example
81359>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// #INCLUDE MERTECH.INC
81359>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// string sDateTime sDatabaseName
81359>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// open ORDERHEA
81359>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// Set_Attribute DF_FIELD_TIME_ON of 30 3 to dfTrue
81359>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// find GE ORDERHEA by recnum
81359>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// move ORDERHEA.ORDER_DATE to sDateTime
81359>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// showln "sDateTime: " sDateTime
81359>>>>>>>>>>>>>Define DF_FIELD_TIME_ON                             For (DF_FIELD_NATIVE_LENGTH+8)
