81359>>>>>>>>>>>>>///     Get_Attribute DF_INDEX_NAME of iFile iIndex to sIndexName
81359>>>>>>>>>>>>>///     Showln "Orderhea.Index." iIndex " : " sIndexName
81359>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// Loop
81359>>>>>>>>>>>>>Define DF_INDEX_NAME                                For (DF_INDEX_KEY_LENGTH+2)
81359>>>>>>>>>>>>>
