82438>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @Param MySQL_Database   Database if   is the File Name
82438>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @Param Var              Variable to hold returned value
82438>>>>>>>>>>>>>
82438>>>>>>>>>>>>>//=============================================================================
82438>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @Name        SET_CLIENT_CFG
82438>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @Description Returns the client character encoding (or encoding ID) information.
82438>>>>>>>>>>>>>///
82438>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @Assumptions
82438>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @Status      Internal
82438>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @Drivers     MySQLFlex and PgFlex
82438>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @VersionNote Last Revised: 2009-09-25 By Ian Smith
82438>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @See
82438>>>>>>>>>>>>>///
82438>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @Syntax SET_CLIENT_CFG [ENCODING | UNIQUE_CHECKS] of <Server> [<MySQL_Database>] to <Value>
