82438>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @Param MySQL_Database   Database if   is the File Name
82438>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @Param Value            Value to set
82438>>>>>>>>>>>>>///
82438>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @Comment ENCODING - Set the Client Encoding
82438>>>>>>>>>>>>>/// @Comment UNIQUE_CHECKS {DFTRUE/DFFALSE} - enable/disable uniqueness checks for secondary indexes in InnoDB tables
82438>>>>>>>>>>>>>
82438>>>>>>>>>>>>>//=============================================================================
