84403>>>>>>>>>>>        Increment iArgnum
84404>>>>>>>>>>>        Get SQLGetArgument iArgnum to sResult
84405>>>>>>>>>>>        Set piLastArgument to iArgnum
84406>>>>>>>>>>>
84406>>>>>>>>>>>        Function_Return sResult
84407>>>>>>>>>>>    End_Function // SQLGetNextArgument
