85013>>>>>>>>>        Move iEN_dbType          to SQLKeywordArray[iSize].iSQLDbType
85014>>>>>>>>>        Move sSQLKeyword         to SQLKeywordArray[iSize].sSQLPhrase
85015>>>>>>>>>        
85015>>>>>>>>>        Set paSQLKeywordArray to SQLKeywordArray
85016>>>>>>>>>    End_Procedure  
