85017>>>>>>>>>    // needs to be done for every keyword group below.
85017>>>>>>>>>    Procedure SetupSQLKeywordArray
85019>>>>>>>>>        tSQLKeyWords[] SQLKeywordArray SQLKeywordArraySorted
85019>>>>>>>>>        tSQLKeyWords[] SQLKeywordArray SQLKeywordArraySorted
85021>>>>>>>>>        
85021>>>>>>>>>        // This should only be called once; but in case it is
85021>>>>>>>>>        // we delete the array first.                        
85021>>>>>>>>>        Set paSQLKeywordArray to SQLKeywordArray 
85022>>>>>>>>>       
85022>>>>>>>>>        // ToDo: *** These SQL Key-words needs to be checked for other backends than MS-SQL! ***
