85244>>>>>>>Class cDbUpdateDB2Driver is a cDbUpdateGenericDatabaseDriver
85245>>>>>>>    Function DbLogin String sConnectionString String sServer String sDatabase Boolean bTrusted String sUserID String sPassword Returns Boolean
85247>>>>>>>        Boolean bLoginSuccessful
85247>>>>>>>        String sDriverID 
85247>>>>>>>        
85247>>>>>>>        Move False to Err
85248>>>>>>>        Get psDriverID to sDriverID
85249>>>>>>>        If (not(Uppercase(sServer) contains "DSN")) Begin
85251>>>>>>>            Move ("DSN=" + sServer) to sServer
85252>>>>>>>        End
85252>>>>>>>>
85252>>>>>>>        Login sServer sUserId sPassword sDriverID
85254>>>>>>>        
85254>>>>>>>        Move (not(Err)) to bLoginSuccessful
85255>>>>>>>        Function_Return bLoginSuccessful
85256>>>>>>>    End_Function
85257>>>>>>>End_Class
