85511>>>>>    Function SQLIniFileDeleteAllConnections Returns Boolean
85513>>>>>        Integer iCount 
85513>>>>>        Boolean bExists 
85513>>>>>        String sSection
85513>>>>>        
85513>>>>>        Move False to Err
85514>>>>>        Move 1 to iCount
85515>>>>>        Get psIniSectionName to sSection
85516>>>>>        Get SectionExists (CS_SQLIniSectionName + String(iCount)) to bExists
85517>>>>>        While (bExists = True)
85521>>>>>            Send DeleteSection (CS_SQLIniSectionName + String(iCount))
85522>>>>>            Increment iCount
85523>>>>>            Get SectionExists (CS_SQLIniSectionName + String(iCount)) to bExists
85524>>>>>        Loop
85525>>>>>>
85525>>>>>        Function_Return (Err = False)
