85527>>>>>    Function SQLIniFileDeleteConnection Integer iItem Returns Boolean
85529>>>>>        Integer iCount 
85529>>>>>        String sSection 
85529>>>>>        Boolean bExists
85529>>>>>        
85529>>>>>        Move False to Err
85530>>>>>        Move 1 to iCount
85531>>>>>        Get psIniSectionName to sSection
85532>>>>>        Get KeyExists sSection CS_SQLIniConnectionIdKeyword to bExists
85533>>>>>        While (bExists = True)
85537>>>>>            If (iCount = iItem) Begin   
85539>>>>>                Send DeleteSection sSection
85540>>>>>//                Set IniFileValue sSection (CS_SQLIniSectionName + String(iCount)) to ""
85540>>>>>                Move 9999 to iCount // Just some ridiculously high number to get out of the loop as we're done.
85541>>>>>            End
85541>>>>>>
85541>>>>>            Increment iCount
85542>>>>>            Get KeyExists sSection (CS_SQLIniSectionName + String(iCount)) to bExists
85543>>>>>        Loop
85544>>>>>>
85544>>>>>        
85544>>>>>        Function_Return (Err = False)
85545>>>>>    End_Function
