88717>>>                            
88717>>>            Case Else     
88717>>>                Error DFERR_PROGRAM "Unsupported driver passed to SqlUtilEnumerateColumns function."
88718>>>>
88718>>>                Case Break
88719>>>        Case End
88719>>>        
88719>>>        Function_Return sReturnArray
88720>>>    End_Function  
