89759>>>    Function _SqlDatabasesArrayMSSQL Returns String[]
89761>>>        String[] sReturnArray
89762>>>        Handle hoSQLHandler
89762>>>        Integer iCount iSize iItem                            
89762>>>        String sServer sUser sPassword 
89762>>>        tSQLConnection SQLConnection
89762>>>        tSQLConnection SQLConnection
89762>>>
89762>>>        Get phoMSSQLHandler to hoSQLHandler
89763>>>        Send Delete_Data    of hoSQLHandler
89764>>>        Get pSQLConnection  of ghoSQLConnectionHandler to SQLConnection
89765>>>
89765>>>        Send Ignore_Error of Error_Object_Id CLIERR_LOGIN_UNSUCCESSFUL
89766>>>        Get EnumerateDatabases of hoSQLHandler SQLConnection.sServer SQLConnection.sUserID SQLConnection.sPassword to iSize
89767>>>        Decrement iSize
89768>>>
89768>>>        For iCount from 0 to iSize
89774>>>>
89774>>>            Get String_Value of hoSQLHandler item iCount to sServer
89775>>>            Move (Trim(sServer)) to sReturnArray[iItem]
89776>>>            Increment iItem
89777>>>        Loop
89778>>>>
89778>>>
89778>>>        Send Trap_Error of Error_Object_Id CLIERR_LOGIN_UNSUCCESSFUL
89779>>>
89779>>>        Function_Return sReturnArray
89780>>>    End_Function
