89891>>>    Function _SqlDatabasesArrayDB2 Returns String[]
89893>>>        String[] sReturnArray
89894>>>        String sDataSource
89894>>>        Handle hoSQLHandler
89894>>>        Integer iItem
89894>>>
89894>>>        Get phoDB2SQLHandler to hoSQLHandler
89895>>>        Send SeedDataSources of hoSQLHandler
89896>>>
89896>>>        Send Ignore_Error of Error_Object_Id CLIERR_LOGIN_UNSUCCESSFUL
89897>>>
89897>>>        Repeat
89897>>>>
89897>>>            Get DataSources of hoSQLHandler to sDataSource
89898>>>            Move (Replaces(",", sDataSource, "")) to sDataSource
89899>>>            Move (Trim(sDataSource)) to sReturnArray[iItem]
89900>>>            Increment iItem
89901>>>        Until (sDataSource = "")
89903>>>
89903>>>        Send Trap_Error of Error_Object_Id CLIERR_LOGIN_UNSUCCESSFUL
89904>>>
89904>>>        Function_Return sReturnArray
89905>>>    End_Function
