89906>>>    Function _SqlDatabasesArrayODBC Returns String[]
89908>>>        String[] sReturnArray
89909>>>        String sDataSource
89909>>>        Handle hoSQLHandler
89909>>>        Integer iItem
89909>>>
89909>>>        Get phoODBCSQLHandler to hoSQLHandler
89910>>>        Send Ignore_Error of Error_Object_Id CLIERR_LOGIN_UNSUCCESSFUL
89911>>>
89911>>>        Send SeedDataSources of hoSQLHandler
89912>>>
89912>>>        Repeat
89912>>>>
89912>>>            Get DataSources of hoSQLHandler to sDataSource
89913>>>            If (Trim(sDataSource) <> "" and not(sDataSource contains "*.")) Begin
89915>>>                Move (Trim(sDataSource)) to sReturnArray[iItem]
89916>>>                Increment iItem
89917>>>            End
89917>>>>
89917>>>        Until (sDataSource = "")
89919>>>
89919>>>        Send Trap_Error of Error_Object_Id CLIERR_LOGIN_UNSUCCESSFUL
89920>>>
89920>>>        Function_Return sReturnArray
