90195>>>    Function ApiTableChangeRelation Handle hTable Handle hToTable Integer iFromField Integer iToField Returns Boolean
90197>>>        Boolean bOK
90197>>>        
90197>>>        Move False to Err
90198>>>        Get AutoConnectionIDLogin to bOK
90199>>>        Open hToTable
