90509>>>    Procedure IncreaseSortBufferSize
90511>>>        String sNull
90511>>>        Integer iSortBufferSize
90511>>>        Boolean bBufferSet
90511>>>    
90511>>>        Move "" to sNull
90512>>>        Move (1024 * 128) to iSortBufferSize
90513>>>        Call_Driver 0 DATAFLEX_ID Function FLEX_SET_MAX_SORT_BUFFER Callback Self Passing sNull sNull iSortBufferSize Result bBufferSet
90518>>>    
90518>>>    End_Procedure     
