91089>>>    // Renames a field for the passed table number & old field name & new field name
91089>>>    // Returns True if no errors occured.
91089>>>    // Sample usage:
91089>>>    //   Get ColumnRename Quote.File_Number "ID#" "ID" to bOK
91089>>>    Function ApiColumnRename Integer hTable String sOldFieldName String sNewFieldName Returns Boolean
91091>>>        Integer iField
91091>>>        Boolean bOK
91091>>>        
91091>>>        Get AutoConnectionIDLogin to bOK
91092>>>        Move False to Err
91093>>>        Open hTable Mode DF_EXCLUSIVE
91095>>>    
91095>>>        Send Ignore_Error of Error_Object_Id DFERR_CANT_FIND_FIELD
91096>>>        Send Ignore_Error of Error_Object_Id DFERR_DUPLICATE_FIELDNAME
91097>>>        Structure_Start hTable
91098>>>            Field_Map hTable sOldFieldName to iField
91100>>>            If (iField > 0) Begin
91102>>>                Set_Attribute DF_FIELD_NAME of hTable iField to sNewFieldName
91105>>>            End
91105>>>>
91105>>>            Else Begin
91106>>>                Move 0 to LastErr
91107>>>                Move False to Err
91108>>>            End
91108>>>>
91108>>>        Structure_End hTable
91110>>>    
91110>>>        Send Trap_Error of Error_Object_Id DFERR_CANT_FIND_FIELD
91111>>>        Send Trap_Error of Error_Object_Id DFERR_DUPLICATE_FIELDNAME
91112>>>        
91112>>>        Function_Return (Err = False)
91113>>>    End_Function
