94586>>>//************************************************************************
94586>>>//
94586>>>// $File name  : StdAbout.pkg
94586>>>// $File title : Standard about object package for VDF
94586>>>// Notice      :
94586>>>// $Author(s)  : John Tuohy
94586>>>//
94586>>>// $Rev History
94586>>>//
94586>>>// JT 06/27/97   File created
94586>>>//************************************************************************
94586>>>
94586>>>// This provides a quick and simple way to create an about package for a program.
94586>>>// You need to create a message inside you client area called Activate_About.
94586>>>// Within this message you should send the message DoAbout passing needed
94586>>>// string information.
94586>>>//
94586>>>//       Procedure Activate_About
94586>>>//           Send DoAbout sTitle sVersion sCopyright sAuthor sBitmap
94586>>>//       End_Procedure
94586>>>//    where: sTitle =     Name of application. If none provided, uses caption
94586>>>//                        bar title
94586>>>//           sVersion   = Version Line. If none provided, will be blank
94586>>>//           sCopyRight = Copyright Line. If none provided, will be blank
94586>>>//           sAuthor    = Author name, blank if none provided
94586>>>//           sBitMap    = Bitmap logo. If none provided, standard VDF bitmap
94586>>>//                        is used.
94586>>>// It is expected that you will place this in your own object package. For
94586>>>// example an order about package may look like this:
94586>>>//
94586>>>//   // OrderAbout.pkg
94586>>>//   Use StdAbout.pkg
94586>>>//   Procedure Activate_About
94586>>>//      String sTitle sCopyright sVersion sAuthor
94586>>>//      Move "My Order Entry System" to sTitle
94586>>>//      Move "Version 2.1" to sVersion
94586>>>//      Move "Copyright 1997, Super Software Inc." to sCopyright
94586>>>//      Move "John Smith"  to sAuthor
94586>>>//      Send DoAbout sTitle sVersion sCopyright sAuthor ""
94586>>>//   end_procedure
94586>>>//   // end of file.
94586>>>
94586>>>Use DfAbout.pkg
Including file: DfAbout.pkg    (C:\Projects\DF18\DbUpdateFramework\AppSrc\DfAbout.pkg)
94586>>>>>//************************************************************************
94586>>>>>// Confidential Trade Secret.
94586>>>>>// Copyright (c) 1997 Data Access Corporation, Miami Florida
94586>>>>>// as an unpublished work.  All rights reserved.
94586>>>>>// DataFlex Is A registered trademark Of Data Access Corporation.
94586>>>>>//
94586>>>>>//************************************************************************
94586>>>>>//************************************************************************
94586>>>>>//
94586>>>>>// $File name  : DfAbout.pkg
94586>>>>>// $File title : About class support
94586>>>>>// Notice      :
94586>>>>>// $Author(s)  : Vincent Oorsprong, Ken Ross
94586>>>>>//
94586>>>>>// $Rev History
94586>>>>>//
94586>>>>>// NGS 08/16/2013 Improved by using a cRichEdit object were the params gets added to.
94586>>>>>//                The objects that previously were popupated with values from the params,
94586>>>>>//                and their corresponding "Procedure Set..." messages, were removed as
94586>>>>>//                the edit object is used instead.
94586>>>>>//                The number of params to the DoAbout procedure was increased to ten, so
94586>>>>>//                it is easier to add whatever extra text strings needed/wanted.
94586>>>>>//                The StdAbout.pkg was also changed for this to work. It allows for an extra
94586>>>>>//                five new params to be passed, but these new params are all optional.
94586>>>>>//                So the interface will work exactly as before - if no extra parameters are passed.
94586>>>>>//                Also added an extra bitmap object to show the "Powered By Visual DataFlex" logo, in
94586>>>>>//                the lower left corner of the About object, beneath the "main" About bitmap.
94586>>>>>//                Note: It is assumed that the bitmap "PoweredByVisualDataFlex.bmp" exists.
94586>>>>>//                The background was changed to clWhite for easier usage of bitmaps. Just set the background
94586>>>>>//                color of your bitmap to white and the bitmap will not look jagged.
94586>>>>>//                If an Internet address is passed as one of the params, it will be underlined and clickable.
94586>>>>>//                An e-mail address can also be passed; e.g. "E-mail: mailto:mail@myemailaccount.com" and will
94586>>>>>//                also be clickable.
94586>>>>>// VOO 02/22/2012 Replaced obsolete code, improved Network_User_Name by asking
94586>>>>>//                Windows for the size first.
94586>>>>>// VOO 07/25/2003 Removed OnResize procedure for sysinfo dialog. Replaced logic
94586>>>>>//                with anchor technique. Removed unnessary property in the
94586>>>>>//                sysinfo dialog. Changed the size Of the about & sysinfo dialog
94586>>>>>//                object To better look in Windows XP. Repositioned the close
94586>>>>>//                button in the sysinfo dialog To line up with the display area
94586>>>>>//                Replaced obsolete code and techniques. Removed dead code.
94586>>>>>// JJT 10/23/2001 removed all ghoworkspace support. Uses app object or nothing
94586>>>>>// SWB 07/19/01   Added support Of the Application object in preference to
94586>>>>>//                the global Workspace object, if it is present
94586>>>>>// JJT 11/05/98   Added version information
94586>>>>>// VOO 29/10/98   Replaced the GetFreeSystemResources for the Win32 variant
94586>>>>>// JJT 7/31/97    Registered Enumerate Workspace so dfabout can exist without
94586>>>>>//                workspace package.
94586>>>>>// JJT 6/27/97    Turned the sysinfo objects into classes so the AboutDialog
94586>>>>>//                class can create this object.
94586>>>>>//                Cleaned up the interface (used correct classes and messages)
94586>>>>>//                Added workspace reporting support To sys-info.
94586>>>>>//                Turned off wrapping in the sys-info editor.
94586>>>>>// KR  ??/??/96   File created
94586>>>>>//************************************************************************
