95112>>>>>    Procedure AppendTextLn String sText
95114>>>>>        String sWorkspaceWSFile
95114>>>>>
95114>>>>>        // Only works for English:
95114>>>>>        If (ghoApplication > 0) Begin
95116>>>>>            If (sText contains "Workspace Name") Begin
95118>>>>>                Move "Workspace Config Filename:" to sText
95119>>>>>                Get psWorkspaceWSFile of (phoWorkspace(ghoApplication)) to sWorkspaceWSFile
95120>>>>>                Move (sText * sWorkspaceWSFile) to sText
95121>>>>>            End
95121>>>>>>
95121>>>>>        End
95121>>>>>>
95121>>>>>        Send AppendText sText
95122>>>>>        Send AppendText (character(10))
95123>>>>>    End_Procedure
