95466>>>>>        End
95466>>>>>>
95466>>>>>    End_Procedure
95467>>>>>
95467>>>>>    //****************************************************************************
95467>>>>>    // $Module type: PROCEDURE
95467>>>>>    // $Module name: Add_Focus
95467>>>>>    // $Author     : VOO
95467>>>>>    // Created     : 24-09-96 @ 19:43
95467>>>>>    //
95467>>>>>    // Description
95467>>>>>    //    During activation we will remove the old information and add the newly
95467>>>>>    //    found systeminformation
95467>>>>>    //
95467>>>>>    // $Rev History
95467>>>>>    //    24-09-96  Module header created
95467>>>>>    //****************************************************************************
95467>>>>>    Procedure Add_Focus Integer hoRoot
95469>>>>>        Forward Send Add_Focus hoRoot
95471>>>>>
95471>>>>>        Send Delete_Data
95472>>>>>
95472>>>>>        Set Changed_State To False
95473>>>>>        Set Read_Only_State To True
95474>>>>>
95474>>>>>        Send Show_Registration
95475>>>>>        Send Show_Drivers
95476>>>>>        Send AppendTextLn ""
95477>>>>>
95477>>>>>        Send Show_ServicePack
95478>>>>>        If (ghoApplication <> 0) Begin
95480>>>>>            Send Show_WorkSpaceInformation
95481>>>>>            Send Show_HelpFile
95482>>>>>            Send AppendTextLn ""
95483>>>>>        End
95483>>>>>>
95483>>>>>        Else Begin
95484>>>>>            Send AppendTextLn ""
95485>>>>>        End
95485>>>>>>
95485>>>>>
95485>>>>>        If (ghoConnection <> 0) Begin
95487>>>>>            Send Show_ConnectionIdInformation
95488>>>>>        End
95488>>>>>>
95488>>>>>        
95488>>>>>        Send Show_Current_User
95489>>>>>        Send Show_Windows_Directory
95490>>>>>        Send Show_Current_Directory
95491>>>>>
95491>>>>>        // This is already shown in the workspace details,
95491>>>>>        // unless no workspace object is present:
95491>>>>>        If (ghoApplication = 0) Begin
95493>>>>>            Send Show_Filelist_Name
95494>>>>>        End
95494>>>>>>
95494>>>>>
95494>>>>>        If (ghoApplication <> 0) Begin
95496>>>>>            Send AppendTextLn ""
95497>>>>>            Send Show_EnterAsTab
95498>>>>>        End
95498>>>>>>
95498>>>>>
95498>>>>>        Send Show_Versions
95499>>>>>        Send Show_Screen_Size
95500>>>>>        Send Show_Page_Size
95501>>>>>        Send Show_Number_Format
95502>>>>>        Send Show_Date_Format
95503>>>>>        Send Show_Lock_Delay
95504>>>>>        Send Show_Lock_Timeout
95505>>>>>        Send Show_Date
95506>>>>>        Send Show_Systemresources
95507>>>>>        Send Beginning_of_Data
95508>>>>>
95508>>>>>        Set Icon to 'default.ico'
95509>>>>>    End_Procedure
95510>>>>>End_Class
