95511>>>>>//****************************************************************************
95511>>>>>// $Module type: OBJECT
95511>>>>>// $Module name: Sysinfo_Dialog
95511>>>>>// $Author     : VOO
95511>>>>>// Created     : 24-09-96 @ 18:47
95511>>>>>//
95511>>>>>// Description
95511>>>>>//    This object shows the systeminformation on the screen
95511>>>>>//
95511>>>>>// $Rev History
95511>>>>>//    24-09-96  Module header created
95511>>>>>//****************************************************************************
95511>>>>>Class SysInfoDialog is a ModalPanel
95512>>>>>    Procedure Construct_Object
95514>>>>>        Forward Send Construct_Object
95516>>>>>
95516>>>>>        Set Label to C_$SystemInformation
95517>>>>>        Set Size to 140 267
95518>>>>>        Set Locate_Mode to CENTER_ON_PARENT
95519>>>>>        Set Border_Style to Border_Thick
95520>>>>>        Set Sysmenu_Icon to False
95521>>>>>
95521>>>>>        // "+1" will make the panel to paint correctly.
95521>>>>>        Set piMinSize to (Hi(Size(Self))) (Low(Size(Self)) +1)
95522>>>>>
95522>>>>>        // 2014-09-14 NGS
95522>>>>>        // Added a container object around the cTexteditor
95522>>>>>        // object to get a border around the text.
95522>>>>>        Object oSysinfoDisplayContainer is a Container3d
95524>>>>>            Set Location to 2 4
95525>>>>>            Set Size to 110 255
95526>>>>>            Set Border_Style to Border_ClientEdge
95527>>>>>            Set Color to clWhite
95528>>>>>            Set peAnchors to anAll
95529>>>>>
95529>>>>>            Object oSysinfoDisplay is a SysInfoDisplay
95531>>>>>            End_Object
95532>>>>>
95532>>>>>        End_Object
95533>>>>>
95533>>>>>        Object oCloseButton is a Button
95535>>>>>            Set Label to C_$Close
95536>>>>>            Set Location to 120 210
95537>>>>>            Set Message item 0 to msg_Close_Panel
95538>>>>>            Set Default_State To True
95539>>>>>            // In case someone likes to make the AboutDialog's Border_Style to thick,
95539>>>>>            // and changes its peAnchors, we might as well prepare this object
95539>>>>>            // for that situation.
95539>>>>>            Set peAnchors to anBottomRight
95540>>>>>        End_Object
95541>>>>>
95541>>>>>        Object oCopyButton is a cCopyEditorContentButton
95543>>>>>            On_Item C_$Copy Send CopyToWindowsClipboard
