96668>>>>>    // Fix for a bug when using manifest files & running Vista and above.
96668>>>>>    // The bug being that the focus rectangle doesn't show.
96668>>>>>    Procedure Page Integer iPageObject
96670>>>>>        Handle hWnd
96670>>>>>        Integer iRet iState iMajorVersion
96670>>>>>
96670>>>>>        Forward Send Page iPageObject
96672>>>>>
96672>>>>>        If (iPageObject) Begin
96674>>>>>            Get Window_Handle to hWnd
96675>>>>>            If (hWnd) Begin
96677>>>>>                Move (SendMessage(hWnd, WM_QUERYUISTATE, 0, 0)) to iRet
96678>>>>>                If (iRet iand UISF_HIDEFOCUS) Begin
96680>>>>>                    Move (UIS_CLEAR + (UISF_HIDEFOCUS * 65536)) to iState
96681>>>>>                    Move (SendMessage(hWnd, WM_UPDATEUISTATE, iState, 0)) to iRet
96682>>>>>                End
96682>>>>>>
96682>>>>>            End
96682>>>>>>
96682>>>>>        End
96682>>>>>>
96682>>>>>    End_Procedure
96683>>>>>
96683>>>>>End_Class
