98238>>>            Move (SizeOfArray(SQLConnectionsArray)) to iSize
98239>>>            Decrement iSize
98240>>>
98240>>>            // Load data to the grid datasource array
98240>>>            For iCount from 0 to iSize
98246>>>>
98246>>>                Get MoveSQLConnectionToGridRow SQLConnectionsArray[iCount] to TheRow
98247>>>                Move TheRow to TheData[iCount]
